{"id": 518, "genre": 1001, "title": "你想在好奇心实验室看到我们做什么实验？", "description": "中秋加国庆假期12天里，让我们替你们做一些很酷的事情！昂！", "record_count": 11705, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606000657rQB1tPC5k2uscbnF.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-09-05T10:00:09Z", "options": [{"id": 12032, "content": "乞丐的一天是怎样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189427}, {"id": 10753, "content": "陪家人，陪闺蜜", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177412}, {"id": 11777, "content": "呃呃呃额额的", "image": "img/option/option/201606042350245OTcxM1s2oPKwzVm.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186950}, {"id": 10754, "content": "验证广告疗效，比如零硅油洗发水之类的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 12034, "content": "每天不喝咖啡会死", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138500}, {"id": 10756, "content": "招募志愿者，光吃青菜，不吃肉。看能坚持多长时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172941}, {"id": 10757, "content": "当什么都没有的时候，我们会做什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177108}, {"id": 12293, "content": "放射性物质分离", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191455}, {"id": 10758, "content": "没有那么长的假期", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173613}, {"id": 11782, "content": "根本就没假期???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 185583}, {"id": 11529, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 10767, "content": "人承受最恶心的兼职是什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 175845}, {"id": 11791, "content": "༺v̎ 还̎ 没̎ ༻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187082}, {"id": 352272, "content": "探测中微子(滑稽)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679797}, {"id": 11281, "content": "啦啦啦", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235024rFu1DXLmGgv3EiVH.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156209}, {"id": 11282, "content": "我不信真的会去做这些实验?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 11538, "content": "比较地区的人类对某一事物态度行为差异！像“人間観察”节目中一个关东关西比较", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235028A9tzxncMvL2q0je3.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177791}, {"id": 10774, "content": "睡眠质量。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177589}, {"id": 11542, "content": "怎么提高销售业绩？怎么能瞬间吸引大量消费群体而不花钱？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183793}, {"id": 12310, "content": "你日思夜想的那个人是否也在无时无刻的想你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 190214}, {"id": 11803, "content": "Ghgf", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187284}, {"id": 11292, "content": "老是牙疼代表想找外遇", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181359}, {"id": 11805, "content": "连续早睡早起二十一天", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235031zZpHQyumXYDhf6rb.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187311}, {"id": 11039, "content": "环游世界只需要一年 而且不用钱", "image": "img/option/option/20160604235027FrBeOhkcq3bjzJMG.jpg", "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 165693}, {"id": 12063, "content": "让一个不爱自己的人爱上自己。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189499}, {"id": 11297, "content": "买台iPhone送我", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181381}, {"id": 11809, "content": "不去透析…出去旅游…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145791}, {"id": 11043, "content": "每天带一个熊孩子去各种各样的地方玩   玩   玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 119096}, {"id": 11812, "content": "用12天", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187360}, {"id": 11301, "content": "招逃BAO间直，時瞯不固定，只要能上網就行，每天50-150，多勞多得，适合空僴较多的大學生、上班族、在家帶小孩的麻麻，加K口《1985392808》？。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 0}, {"id": 11557, "content": "换个性别生活12天", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184058}, {"id": 11559, "content": "不吃辛辣食物（除了大蒜）?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 128917}, {"id": 11815, "content": "到国外一个人生存", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187360}, {"id": 10794, "content": "荒野生存我报名", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160915}, {"id": 11050, "content": "想跟你們一起做實驗", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173136}, {"id": 10795, "content": "不撸??", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177627}, {"id": 11051, "content": "找个爱人", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117457}, {"id": 11564, "content": "代课业务，有无意见", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184071}, {"id": 11820, "content": "敢不敢老老实实回家陪父母？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186305}, {"id": 10797, "content": "12天的假期里不睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132807}, {"id": 11567, "content": "怎么看详情啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181054}, {"id": 10800, "content": "成為我的鏟?官 (˶‾᷄ ⁻̫ ‾᷅˵)", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211054w6MlCxYphRcZFEgH.jpg", "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155388}, {"id": 11824, "content": "泡图书馆。。。好无聊的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 186982}, {"id": 10801, "content": "环球旅行！", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177725}, {"id": 11057, "content": "上街发传单，挣钱社交两不误!", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179279}, {"id": 10802, "content": "禁欲十二天，拒绝啪啪啪。", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177730}, {"id": 10804, "content": "坐一列横跨中国大陆的火车?超过24小时都呆车上的那种?～然后和车上的每个人拍一张合照?", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177733}, {"id": 11575, "content": "裸着，在家不出门，并每天拍照发粗来～", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 183814}, {"id": 11320, "content": "后来进来的人们总是会跟着赞，“赞”最多的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181645}, {"id": 11321, "content": "主动要求加班不放假", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181673}]}